### [APPROVE] Registry Integration (Lines 121-129 in `registry.ts`)

**Well Done**: The three handlers are correctly registered in `defaultActionRegistry` with consistent naming (`setValue`, `setComputed`, `useAll`). Matches pattern from navigation handlers.

